#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:5
msgid ""
"An *inventory adjustment*, or inventory audit, is the process of verifying "
"the physical stock of products against the quantities recorded in the "
"database. Regular audits ensure accurate inventory records, prevent stock "
"discrepancies, and maintain efficient operations. In a warehouse setting, "
"managers typically assign inventory counts to employees, who then walk to "
"designated locations, scan product barcodes, and adjust quantities as needed."
msgstr ""
"Um *ajuste de inventĂĄrio*, ou auditoria de inventĂĄrio, Ă© o processo de "
"verificaĂ§ĂŁo do estoque fĂ­sico de produtos em relaĂ§ĂŁo Ă s quantidades "
"registradas na base de dados. Auditorias regulares garantem registros de "
"inventĂĄrio precisos, previnem discrepĂąncias de estoque e mantĂȘm operaĂ§Ă”es "
"eficientes. Em um ambiente de armazĂ©m, os gerentes normalmente atribuem "
"contagens de inventĂĄrio aos funcionĂĄrios, que entĂŁo caminham atĂ© os locais "
"designados, escaneiam cĂłdigos de barras de produtos e ajustam as quantidades "
"conforme necessĂĄrio."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/barcode/operations/adjustments.rst:11
msgid ""
"Inventory adjustments can be completed through the **Barcode** application "
"using a compatible scanner, or the Odoo mobile app."
msgstr ""
"Os ajustes de inventĂĄrio podem ser concluĂ­dos atravĂ©s do aplicativo **CĂłdigo "
"de Barras** usando um scanner compatĂ­vel, ou o aplicativo mĂłvel do Odoo."

