#~ "A Frankie's Consignment Shop compra suĂ©teres ao custo, "
#~ "ou :guilabel:`Valor unitĂĄrio`, de `5,00` dĂłlares. Pela primeira vez, a "
#~ "Frankie's compra e recebe uma :guilabel:`Quantidade` de `100,00` suĂ©teres "
#~ "em uma movimentaĂ§ĂŁo de estoque, depois revende e entrega `-10,00` "
#~ "suĂ©teres em uma segunda movimentaĂ§ĂŁo de estoque."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In the first stock move line item, the :guilabel:`Remaining Quantity` "
#~ "will change from `100.00` to `90.00`, once the second stock move is "
#~ "recorded. This change reflects that, although 100 sweaters were "
#~ "originally purchased, only 90 of those sweaters remain in stock and "
#~ "should be counted in the valuation. Similarly, the :guilabel:`Remaining "
#~ "Value` will drop from `$500.00` to `$450.00`. The :guilabel:`Total Value` "
#~ "will remain at `$500.00`, regardless of subsequent transactions."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "No primeiro item de linha de movimentaĂ§ĂŁo de estoque, "
#~ "o :guilabel:`Quantidade restante` serĂĄ alterado de `100,00` para `90,00`, "
